.TH PASSPORT-UNLOCKER-GUI 1 "July 2026" "passport-unlocker 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
passport-unlocker-gui \- graphical unlocker for compatible WD My Passport drives
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B passport-unlocker-gui
.RI [ --monitor ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B passport-unlocker-gui
starts the GTK 4 and Libadwaita desktop interface. It discovers candidate
devices, accepts a drive password, and requests the restricted privileged
helper through Polkit.
.PP
Run the GUI as the desktop user, not with
.BR sudo (8).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --monitor
Remain in the user session as the XDG autostart monitor and present the window
when a candidate device is detected.
.SH SECURITY
Passwords are not saved. The password field is cleared after an operation.
The application is unofficial and is not affiliated with or endorsed by
Western Digital.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR passport-unlocker (1),
.BR pkexec (1)

